== 使用方法 ==
<code>{{tlp|Link if equal|string1|string2|link|caption}}</code> gives
* "[[link|caption]]" (i.e. a link) if <code>string1</code> and <code>string2</code> are equal,
* "caption" (i.e. no link) if they are not.

== 另见 ==
* {{tl|Link if not equal}} – a template with an opposite behavior
* {{tl|Link if exists}}
* {{tl|Link if not current}}

